item.title: CVE-2022-3511|2024-08-03T01:14:02.488Z -- unknown -- awesome%20support
item.description: The Awesome Support WordPress plugin before 6.1.2 does not ensure that the exported tickets archive to be downloaded belongs to the user making the request, allowing a low privileged user, such as subscriber to download arbitrary exported tickets via an IDOR vector
